.parent.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntFlex_0\").getChild(\"cntEndDate\").getChild(\"DateTimeInput\").props.value\n\tif edate \u003d\u003d \u0027\u0027 or str(edate).upper() \u003d\u003d \u0027None\u0027.upper():\n\t\tself.view.params.EDate \u003d None\n\telse:\n\t\tself.view.params.EDate \u003d self.parent.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntFlex_0\").getChild(\"cntEndDate\").getChild(\"DateTimeInput\").props.value\n\t\n\tsystem.perspective.print(\"params added\")"
